{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.007.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Villes b\u00e2ties par Salomon<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-11: cf. 1 R 9:10-24.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Au bout de vingt ans, pendant lesquels Salomon b\u00e2tit la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et sa propre maison,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.2","name":"2 Chroniques 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.7.22","name":"2 Chroniques 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.7.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>il reconstruisit les villes que lui donna Huram et y \u00e9tablit des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.3","name":"2 Chroniques 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.1","name":"2 Chroniques 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Salomon marcha contre Hamath, vers Tsoba, et s\u2019en empara.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.4","name":"2 Chroniques 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.2","name":"2 Chroniques 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il b\u00e2tit Thadmor au d\u00e9sert, et toutes les villes servant de magasins en Hamath.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.5","name":"2 Chroniques 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.3","name":"2 Chroniques 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il b\u00e2tit Beth-Horon la haute et Beth-Horon la basse, villes fortes, ayant des murs, des portes et des barres;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.6","name":"2 Chroniques 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.4","name":"2 Chroniques 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Baalath, et toutes les villes servant de magasins et lui appartenant, toutes les villes pour les chars, les villes pour la cavalerie, et tout ce qu\u2019il plut \u00e0 Salomon de b\u00e2tir \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, au Liban, et dans tout le pays dont il \u00e9tait le souverain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.7","name":"2 Chroniques 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.5","name":"2 Chroniques 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Tout le peuple qui \u00e9tait rest\u00e9 des H\u00e9thiens, des Amor\u00e9ens, des Ph\u00e9r\u00e9ziens, des H\u00e9viens et des J\u00e9busiens, ne faisant point partie d\u2019Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.6","name":"2 Chroniques 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>leurs descendants qui \u00e9taient rest\u00e9s apr\u00e8s eux dans le pays et que les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl n\u2019avaient pas d\u00e9truits, Salomon les leva comme gens de corv\u00e9e, ce qu\u2019ils ont \u00e9t\u00e9 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.9","name":"2 Chroniques 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.7","name":"2 Chroniques 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Salomon n\u2019employa comme esclave pour ses travaux aucun des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; car ils \u00e9taient des hommes de guerre, ses chefs, ses officiers, les commandants de ses chars et de sa cavalerie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.10","name":"2 Chroniques 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Les chefs plac\u00e9s par le roi Salomon \u00e0 la t\u00eate du peuple, et charg\u00e9s de le surveiller, \u00e9taient au nombre de deux cent cinquante.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.11","name":"2 Chroniques 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.9","name":"2 Chroniques 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Salomon fit monter la fille de Pharaon de la cit\u00e9 de David dans la maison qu\u2019il lui avait b\u00e2tie; car il dit: Ma femme n\u2019habitera pas dans la maison de David, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, parce que les lieux o\u00f9 est entr\u00e9e l\u2019arche de l\u2019\u00c9ternel sont saints.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.12","name":"2 Chroniques 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.10","name":"2 Chroniques 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Navires envoy\u00e9s \u00e0 Ophir<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-18: cf. 1 R 9:25-28; 22:49, 50.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Alors Salomon offrit des holocaustes \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel sur l\u2019autel de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qu\u2019il avait construit devant le portique.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.13","name":"2 Chroniques 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.11","name":"2 Chroniques 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Il offrait ce qui \u00e9tait prescrit par Mo\u00efse pour chaque jour, pour les sabbats, pour les nouvelles lunes, et pour les f\u00eates, trois fois l\u2019ann\u00e9e, \u00e0 la f\u00eate des pains sans levain, \u00e0 la f\u00eate des semaines, et \u00e0 la f\u00eate des tabernacles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.14","name":"2 Chroniques 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.12","name":"2 Chroniques 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il \u00e9tablit dans leurs fonctions, telles que les avait r\u00e9gl\u00e9es David, son p\u00e8re, les classes des sacrificateurs selon leur office, les L\u00e9vites selon leur charge, consistant \u00e0 c\u00e9l\u00e9brer l\u2019\u00c9ternel et \u00e0 faire jour par jour le service en pr\u00e9sence des sacrificateurs, et les portiers distribu\u00e9s \u00e0 chaque porte d\u2019apr\u00e8s leurs classes; car ainsi l\u2019avait ordonn\u00e9 David, homme de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.15","name":"2 Chroniques 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.13","name":"2 Chroniques 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>On ne s\u2019\u00e9carta point de l\u2019ordre du roi pour les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites, ni pour aucune chose, ni pour ce qui concernait les tr\u00e9sors.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.16","name":"2 Chroniques 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.14","name":"2 Chroniques 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Ainsi fut dirig\u00e9e toute l\u2019\u0153uvre de Salomon, jusqu\u2019au jour o\u00f9 la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut fond\u00e9e et jusqu\u2019\u00e0 celui o\u00f9 elle fut termin\u00e9e. La maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut donc achev\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.17","name":"2 Chroniques 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.15","name":"2 Chroniques 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.008.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Salomon partit alors pour \u00c9tsjon-Gu\u00e9ber et pour \u00c9loth, sur les bords de la mer, dans le pays d\u2019\u00c9dom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.18","name":"2 Chroniques 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.16","name":"2 Chroniques 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.18","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 8:18","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.008.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.009.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.8.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et Huram lui envoya par ses serviteurs des navires et des serviteurs connaissant la mer. Ils all\u00e8rent avec les serviteurs de Salomon \u00e0 Ophir, et ils y prirent quatre cent cinquante talents d\u2019or, qu\u2019ils apport\u00e8rent au roi Salomon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8","name":"2 Chroniques 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.9.1","name":"2 Chroniques 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.9.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.8.17","name":"2 Chroniques 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.8.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb5ddaec4.84188388');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5ddaec4.84188388\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb5ddaec4.84188388","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb5ddaec4.84188388'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5ddaec4.84188388\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}